---
layout: base.njk
title: Our Team
description: Meet the Ace Strategies team. Decades of experience in senior government, media, and private sector roles delivering impactful solutions.
active_nav: /team/
---

<section class="team-hero" data-theme="dark">
  <div class="hero-media">
    <video autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata">
      <source src="/assets/repository/videos/vid-hero-first.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1 class="team-hero-title">Experience, integrity, and <br><span>strategic insight.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Our team combines decades of experience in senior government, media, and private sector roles to deliver impactful solutions.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="capability-matrix-section" data-theme="light">
  <div class="matrix-container">
    <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
      <span class="section-label">Collective Strength</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Why We Lead</h2>
      <div class="section-divider"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="matrix-grid">
      <div class="matrix-card">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined matrix-icon">policy</span>
        <h3 class="matrix-title">Government Insight</h3>
        <p class="matrix-desc">Deep networks within state, federal and international governments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="matrix-card">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined matrix-icon">factory</span>
        <h3 class="matrix-title">Industry Expertise</h3>
        <p class="matrix-desc">Understands the national industrial sector and global opportunities.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="matrix-card">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined matrix-icon">crisis_alert</span>
        <h3 class="matrix-title">Crisis Management</h3>
        <p class="matrix-desc">Battle-tested strategies for protecting reputation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="matrix-card">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined matrix-icon">groups</span>
        <h3 class="matrix-title">Community Trust</h3>
        <p class="matrix-desc">Proven methodologies for earning social licence.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="team-section" data-theme="light">
  <div class="team-container">
    {% for member in team %}
    <div class="profile-block" id="{{ member.id }}">
      <div class="profile-image-wrapper">
        <img src="{{ member.image_profile }}" alt="{{ member.image_alt_profile }}" class="profile-img">
      </div>
      <div class="profile-content">
        <h2>{{ member.name }}</h2>
        <span class="profile-role">{{ member.role }}</span>
        <div class="profile-bio">
          {% for para in member.bio_paragraphs %}
          <p>{{ para }}</p>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section" data-theme="dark">
  <div class="cta-content">
    <h2 class="cta-title">Partner with <span class="highlight">Experience.</span></h2>
    <p class="cta-sub">Navigate complexity with a team that has been there before.</p>
    <a href="/contact/" class="cta-button">Contact our team</a>
  </div>
</section>